OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1774469468
OL,3,CFM Eluned Morgan on course to lose
OL,4,Cseat in Senedd Election - ITV Wales
OL,5,Cpoll
OL,7,FFirst Minister Eluned Morgan is on
OL,8,Fcourse to lose her seat in the
OL,9,Fupcoming Senedd Election, according to
OL,10,Fthe latest ITV Cymru Wales opinion
OL,11,Fpoll.
OL,13,FIt's the latest blow for Welsh Labour
OL,14,Fwhich have landed in third place after
OL,15,Fhitting their lowest point in
OL,16,FJanuary's poll.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1774469468
OL,3,CFM Eluned Morgan on course to lose
OL,4,Cseat in Senedd Election - ITV Wales
OL,5,Cpoll
OL,7,FDespite a drop in vote share to 33%
OL,8,FPlaid Cymru is still on course to be
OL,9,Fthe largest party with a seat
OL,10,Fprojection suggesting it could win 43
OL,11,Fseats, leaving Rhun ap Iorwerth six
OL,12,Fshort of forming an overall majority
OL,13,Fin the Senedd.
OL,15,FReform UK has closed the gap on Plaid
OL,16,Fafter increasing its share to 27%
OL,17,Fsince our last poll which, in this
OL,18,Fscenario, would translate to 30
OL,19,Fmembers of the Senedd.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
