CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1774469468
OL,3,CFM Eluned Morgan on course to lose
OL,4,Cseat in Senedd Election - ITV Wales
OL,5,Cpoll
OL,7,FWith just over six weeks until the
OL,8,Felection, YouGov poll for ITV Wales in
OL,9,Fpartnership with Cardiff University -
OL,10,Fthe largest so far - has applied the
OL,11,Flatest MRP modelling to offer a
OL,12,Fpredicted breakdown of how many seats
OL,13,Feach party will win in each of the 16
OL,14,Fnew constituencies.
OL,16,FAn increase for Labour puts them third
OL,17,Fon 13% and resulting in 12 seats,
OL,18,Fmeaning Eluned Morgan's party would
OL,19,Fnot elect anyone in four
OL,20,Fconstituencies, including her own in
OL,21,FCeredgion Penfro.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1774469468
OL,3,CFM Eluned Morgan on course to lose
OL,4,Cseat in Senedd Election - ITV Wales
OL,5,Cpoll
OL,7,F"This poll points to a narrowing in
OL,8,Fthe race for largest party between
OL,9,FPlaid Cymru and Reform UK since the
OL,10,Flast ITV Cymru poll," says Dr Jac
OL,11,FLarner, from Cardiff University's
OL,12,FWelsh Governance Centre, "but adds
OL,13,Ffurther evidence that the contest to
OL,14,Fform the next government is firmly
OL,15,Fbetween these two parties.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1774469468
OL,3,CFM Eluned Morgan on course to lose
OL,4,Cseat in Senedd Election - ITV Wales
OL,5,Cpoll
OL,7,F"Plaid Cymru remain in the strongest
OL,8,Fposition - not only are they projected
OL,9,Fto be the largest party, but if short
OL,10,Fof a majority they have more options
OL,11,Ffor coalition partners. Reform faces
OL,12,Ffar greater constraints, yet there
OL,13,Fshould be no mistake: winning a third
OL,14,Fof seats would represent a remarkable
OL,15,Fresult.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1774469468
OL,3,CFM Eluned Morgan on course to lose
OL,4,Cseat in Senedd Election - ITV Wales
OL,5,Cpoll
OL,7,F"The poll also suggests that the race
OL,8,Ffor third place is now firmly between
OL,9,FLabour and the Greens. Labour's
OL,10,Fposition has improved marginally since
OL,11,FJanuary, supported by improving
OL,12,Funderlying evaluations of UK
OL,13,Fgovernment performance and a modest
OL,14,Frecovery in ratings for Keir Starmer
OL,15,Ffrom their historic January low.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1774469468
OL,3,CFM Eluned Morgan on course to lose
OL,4,Cseat in Senedd Election - ITV Wales
OL,5,Cpoll
OL,7,F"The Greens will be encouraged that
OL,8,Fthey have maintained a strong position
OL,9,Fin Wales, building on their success in
OL,10,FEngland. Notably, their rise does not
OL,11,Fappear to have come at Plaid Cymru's
OL,12,Fexpense, suggesting the two parties
OL,13,Fare drawing support from largely
OL,14,Fseparate pools of voters. The results
OL,15,Falso point clearly to a near-
OL,16,Fsupermajority for progressive parties
OL,17,Fin the Senedd."
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1774469468
OL,3,CFM Eluned Morgan on course to lose
OL,4,Cseat in Senedd Election - ITV Wales
OL,5,Cpoll
OL,7,FWhilst the Greens' 12% could yield
OL,8,Fthem ten seats, the Conservatives are
OL,9,Fon the verge of being wiped out in the
OL,10,FSenedd with current polling at 7%
OL,11,Fresulting in just one seat in Clwyd
OL,12,Ffor leader Darren Millar.
OL,14,FThis set of figures means 5% for the
OL,15,FLib Dems would leave Jane Dodds party
OL,16,Fwith no representation in the Senedd
OL,17,Ffrom May.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1774469468
OL,3,CFM Eluned Morgan on course to lose
OL,4,Cseat in Senedd Election - ITV Wales
OL,5,Cpoll
OL,7,FDr Larner said: "For the Conservatives
OL,8,Fand the Liberal Democrats, this poll
OL,9,Fillustrates how the new electoral
OL,10,Fsystem can punish even small changes
OL,11,Fin vote share with disproportionate
OL,12,Flosses in seats.
OL,14,F"For the Conservatives, a modest
OL,15,Ffurther shift of voters towards Reform
OL,16,Fcould result in near-electoral wipeout
OL,17,F` and, somewhat ironically,
OL,18,Fpotentially reduce Reform's own
OL,19,Fcapacity to form a government.
OL,26,@oD@QOUvD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
