PN,46610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1774469468
OL,3,CFM Eluned Morgan on course to lose
OL,4,Cseat in Senedd Election - ITV Wales
OL,5,Cpoll
OL,7,F"For the Liberal Democrats, even
OL,8,Fwithout significant losses among their
OL,9,Fexisting Welsh voters, a marginally
OL,10,Fstronger Labour showing combined with
OL,11,Fa solid Green performance effectively
OL,12,Fraises the threshold of votes required
OL,13,Fto win a seat in any constituency
OL,14,Facross Wales."
OL,16,FWhen looking at Westminster voting
OL,17,Fintentions, Plaid Cymru continues to
OL,18,Fbe the most popular with an increase
OL,19,Ffor the Greens and very small drop in
OL,20,Fsupport for Reform.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@NO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
