PN,46611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1774469468
OL,3,CFM Eluned Morgan on course to lose
OL,4,Cseat in Senedd Election - ITV Wales
OL,5,Cpoll
OL,7,FAdrian Masters, ITV Cymru Wales'
OL,8,FPolitical Editor, said: "Welsh
OL,9,Fpolitics continues in a state of flux.
OL,10,FThe headline figures in our latest
OL,11,Fpoll may be broadly similar to recent
OL,12,Fsurveys, but there are differences in
OL,13,Fthe detail which show that the picture
OL,14,Fis far from settled.
OL,26,@pD@YOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1774469468
OL,3,CFM Eluned Morgan on course to lose
OL,4,Cseat in Senedd Election - ITV Wales
OL,5,Cpoll
OL,7,F"The two front runners will hope the
OL,8,Fchanges they've seen in it will
OL,9,Fgalvanise their supporters, while the
OL,10,Ftwo historically-big parties will
OL,11,Fcontinue to hope the picture isn't as
OL,12,Fbleak as it appears. Certainly for
OL,13,FLabour a slight increase and a halt in
OL,14,Fa Green surge provides crumbs of hope.
OL,16,F"A radically different Senedd is on
OL,17,Fits way, with a large number of new
OL,18,Fmembers and every sign that there will
OL,19,Fbe a change of government. The stakes
OL,20,Fcouldn't be much higher."
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@AOU|D@YO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G12/14
