OL,7,FFind out how our poll translates into
OL,8,Fseats in your constituency using our
OL,9,Finteractive map
OL,11,F*For YouGov's Senedd Voting Intentions
OL,12,FMRP Model there was a full nationally
OL,13,Frepresentative sample of 2,978 adults
OL,14,Fin Wales aged 16+, of which 2,199 gave
OL,15,Fa voting intention. Fieldwork was
OL,16,Fundertaken between 9th March and 18th
OL,17,FMarch 2026. For YouGov's Westminster
OL,18,FVoting Intentions MRP Model the total
OL,19,Fsample size was 1,082 adults (+18).
OL,20,FFieldwork was undertaken between 12th
OL,21,F- 19th March 2026.
